hestral Suite\r\n13. John Williams - Album Finish\r\n</pre>'),
(2, 'Star_Wars_Episode_2_Atacke_of_the_Clone.jpg', 'Фильм 2002 года.', 'Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones', 'MIDNIGHT', '^_^', '', '<pre>\r\nТреклист:\r\nCD 1 (Original Realise)\r\n01. John Williams - Star Wars Main Title And Ambush on Coruscant\r\n02. John Williams - Love Theme from Attack of the Clones\r\n03. John Williams - Zam the Assassin and The Chase Through Coruscant\r\n04. John Williams - Yoda and the Younglings\r\n05. John Williams - Departing Coruscant\r\n06. John Williams - Anakin and PadmPi\r\n07. John Williams - Jango''s Escape\r\n08. John Williams - The Meadow Picnic\r\n09. John Williams - Bounty Hunter''s Pursuit\r\n10. John Williams - Return to Tatooine\r\n11. John Williams - The Tusken Camp and The Homestead\r\n12. John Williams - Love Pledge and The Arena\r\n13. John Williams - Confrontation with Count Dooku and Finale\r\n14. John Williams - On the Conveyor Belt\r\nCD 2 (The Extended Edition)\r\n01. John Williams - 20th Century Fox Fanfare\r\n02. John Williams - Star Wars Main Titles\r\n03. John Williams - Old Friends\r\n04. John Williams - Assasination Attempt And Speeder Chase\r\n05. John Williams - The Chase Through Coruscant Continues\r\n06. John Williams - The Assasin''s Demise\r\n07. John Williams - Growing Up\r\n08. John Williams - Departing Coruscant\r\n09. John Williams - Dex''s Diner\r\n10. John Williams - Yoda And The Younglings\r\n11. John Williams - Arrival At Kamino\r\n12. John Williams - Forbidden Kiss\r\n13. John Williams - The Clone Army\r\n14. John Williams - The Meadow Picnic\r\n15. John Williams - Meeting Jango Fett\r\n16. John Williams - Anakin And Padme\r\n17. John Williams - Mystery Of The Clones\r\n18. John Williams - Tatooine Resolution\r\n19. John Williams - Jango vs. Obi-Wan\r\n20. John Williams - Bounty Hunter''s Pursuit\r\n21. John Williams - Anakin''s Search\r\n22. John Williams - Dark Deeds\r\nCD 3 (The Extended Edition)\r\n01. John Williams - Anakin''s Confession\r\n02. John Williams - Emergency Powers\r\