(3, 'Star_Wars_Episode_3_Revenge_of_the_Sith.jpg', 'Фильм 2005 года', 'Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith', 'asas', '', '', '<pre>\r\nТреклист:\r\nCD 1 (OST)\r\n01. John Williams - Star Wars And The Revenge Of The Sith\r\n02. John Williams - Anakin''s Dream\r\n03. John Williams - Battle Of The Heroes\r\n04. John Williams - Anakin''s Betrayal\r\n05. John Williams - General Grievous\r\n06. John Williams - Palpatine''s Teachings\r\n07. John Williams - Grievous And The Droids\r\n08. John Williams - Padme''s Ruminations\r\n09. John Williams - Anakin Vs. Obi-Wan\r\n10. John Williams - Anakin''s Dark Deeds\r\n11. John Williams - Enter Lord Vader\r\n12. John Williams - The Immolation Scene\r\n13. John Williams - Grievous Speaks To Lord Sidious\r\n14. John Williams - The Birth Of The Twins And Padme''s Destiny\r\n15. John Williams - A New Hope And End Credits\r\nCD 2 (The Extended Edition)\r\n01. John Williams - 20th Century Fox Fanfare\r\n02. John Williams - Star Wars Main Title / Battle Over Coruscant\r\n03. John Williams - Enter General Grevious\r\n04. John Williams - Dooku''s Entrance\r\n05. John Williams - Escape With The Chancellor\r\n06. John Williams - Jedi vs. Droids\r\n07. John Williams - Another Happy Landing\r\n08. John Williams - The Chancellor''s Arrival\r\n09. John Williams - Lovers'' Reunion\r\n10. John Williams - Travelling To Utapau / Anakin''s Dream\r\n11. John Williams - Dreams And Visions\r\n12. John Williams - Be Careful Of Your Friend\r\n13. John Williams - On The Council\r\n14. John Williams - We''re At War\r\n15. John Williams - The Prophecy\r\n16. John Williams - The Tragedy Of Darth Plagueis\r\n17. John Williams - Kashyyyk\r\n18. John Williams - Goodbye Old Friend\r\n19. John Williams - Daydreams\r\n20. John Williams - Arrival At Utapau\r\n21. John Williams - Riding Boga\r\n22. John Williams - Crushing The Droids\r\n23. John Williams - Obi-Wan vs. Grievous\r\n24. John Williams - Jedi War Council\r\n25. John Williams - Palpatine''s Seducti